Every long-term care facility shall post in a conspicuous place, accessible to residents, employees and visitors the following:
A copy of the long-term care facility's current license;
The name, address, and current telephone number of the current long-term care ombudsman in the cabinet;
A copy of the statement required by subsection (1) of KRS 216.545; and
A list of the material available for public inspection required by KRS 216.547.
